item.title: CVE-2020-5144|2024-08-04T08:22:08.672Z -- sonicwall -- sonicwall%20global%20vpn%20client
item.description: SonicWall Global VPN client version 4.10.4.0314 and earlier allows unprivileged windows user to elevate privileges to SYSTEM through loaded process hijacking vulnerability.

item.title: CVE-2020-5145|2024-08-04T08:22:09.084Z -- sonicwall -- sonicwall%20global%20vpn%20client
item.description: SonicWall Global VPN client version 4.10.4.0314 and earlier have an insecure library loading (DLL hijacking) vulnerability. Successful exploitation could lead to remote code execution in the target system.
